{"tid":1083192,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)白事可樂 地心浩劫 亡命快遞","createTime":"2019-03-29T12:33:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-29T17:09:09.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7e70a3bcddbe6d3aa2d249e9a05f804426f2e219","tid":1083192,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T12:33:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=tn6C2tKLXSv13zRFu6un7Sukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=0c9e4043\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=tn6C2tKLXSv13zRFu6un7Sukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=9aa10dda\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=tn6C2tKLXSv13zRFu6un7Sukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=f79a1647\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/9/9f/Newworldwarzpostersmall.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F9%2F9f%2FNewworldwarzpostersmall.jpg&h=c21a4019&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/4R6_QYkcPmo/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2F4R6_QYkcPmo%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=026f6108&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/e/e6/Premium_rush.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fe%2Fe6%2FPremium_rush.jpg&h=11de8bcc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.前聯合國調查員傑瑞&middot;藍恩與自己的妻子凱倫和兩個女兒瑞秋與康妮，愉快的在擁擠的費城市區公路上行車，但一分鐘內就有多架直升機從空中飛過，而新聞上一直在談論關於台灣爆發的狂犬病毒。突然間，公路前方發生了爆炸，而公路上執勤的警察當場被失控的垃圾車撞死，傑瑞跟隨垃圾車的行進路線離開公路，之後與一輛失控的救護車發生相撞。傑瑞與凱倫回過神來後，帶著女兒們丟下汽車逃跑，而廣場上也轉眼間出現了幾百名瘋狂咬人的殭屍，而傑瑞與家人逃離時親眼看到一名被殭屍咬到的人，在十二秒之內也淪為了一個殭屍，後來與家人開著一輛房車逃離了城市。不到兩小時，費城淪陷，美軍阻止殭屍的軍事行動全部以失敗告終...<br />\n<br />\n2.電影講述地球的核心因不明原因停止轉動，以致電磁場減弱。在失去地磁的保護下，地球會遭到致命的高能宇宙微波輻射襲擊，造成災難。此時有6人組成團隊，駕駛一艘名為「維吉爾號」的潛地艇，鑽進熾熱地函，放置並引爆核彈，使地核再次轉動<br />\n<br />\n3.威利（喬瑟夫&middot;高登-李維飾演）是紐約市首屈一指的自行車快遞，他的前女友凡妮莎（丹妮雅&middot;拉米瑞茲飾演）也是個自行車快遞。她的室友妮瑪（鍾潔咪飾演）將她兩年內拚死拚活兼三份工作所存下來的錢，交給了中國人蛇販子－梁先生（區亨利飾演）換來一張「票券」，妮瑪須想辦法在限定時間內將「票券」交給一名陳大姐，才可讓妮瑪的母親及兒子能藉由陳大姐的貨船從中國來到美國<br />\n<br />\n8 40PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=tn6C2tKLXSv13zRFu6un7Sukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=e94f0d4f\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=tn6C2tKLXSv13zRFu6un7Sukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=5f7677f2\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6253f858bd5bdf15f14809ad6cb61bb18fd7860c","tid":1083192,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T12:34:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f50f58e0195a5dd3c6dd637a9a7f6009e97babf","tid":1083192,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T13:25:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"293c0d09171bdd1582218f0e3e12547b433f8524","tid":1083192,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T15:06:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"794a79390ec5c0823d8f4971f80a5f02ab48c040","tid":1083192,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T16:28:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e70c90de9b35df7407afbf3c4569fb8a226b6cc","tid":1083192,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T17:09:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}